channel.description:
[center][font=impact][size=36pt]Divine Scape[/size][/font] [URL=http://"http://divinescape.site90.net"]Website[/URL] | [URL=http://"http://divinescape.site90.net/services.html"]Webclient[/URL] | [URL=http://"https://dl.dropbox.com/u/94067307/DivineScape.jar"]Download Client[/URL]
[B]Information:[/B] DivineScape is a fun server, where you can basically login and start having fun straight away! Whether you are a experienced PKer or if you just want to go for max stats, DivineScape is the perfect server for every type of person.! This server is filled with content and it's enjoyable! We have a nice and friendly community, and at DivineScape, It is run by you guys! DivineScape is a unique server due to the fact that we have a friendly and charming community. DivineScape has the potential to be one of the best servers in history, it's just we need more players! If you give us a chance, I PROMISE you, you won't be disappointed.
[B]Server Features:[/B] Functional magics. Near-perfect combat. Bug free mini-games. Great training facilities. Various PKing teleports. All skills functional. Realistic economy. Active and friendly staff. Items on death interface. Curses working. Working hand cannon w/ special. Working EXP counter. Vote for rewards system. Player and NPC clipping. Flawless switching. Grand Exchange (60% done). 100% Special Attack. 5 Awesome Places to Train. 100% RS music Full HD. 24/26 Fully working skills.
